(1205, 40, 'To ra mi trng cho cc h iu hnh khc nhau trn mt my tnh thc s nh th no?', 'Bng cch s dng my o  chy tng h iu hnh c lp, cho php nhiu mi trng ng thi m khng nh hng ln nhau.', 'Bng cch chuyn tt c tc v ra ngoi ht nhn, nhng khng cn my o.', 'Bng cch gi ht nhn ln v khng s dng m hnh Client-Server.', 'Bng cch ch chy mt h iu hnh trn phn cng thc s m khng cn phn mm gi lp.', 'Bng cch s dng my o  chy tng h iu hnh c lp, cho php nhiu mi trng ng thi m khng nh hng ln nhau.', 'evaluate', '2025-04-16 03:38:40', '2025-04-16 03:38:40'),
